    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>/authors/admin/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/authors/admin/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I am an Associate Research Scientist at 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.yale.edu&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Yale University&lt;/a&gt;. I am interested in identifying physiological mechanisms of brain function, in particular, the neural substrates of flexible, goal-directed behavior. For this, I build neural network and reinforcement learning models.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In July 2020, I will start my own Lab at the 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.upv.es&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Universitat Politècnica de València&lt;/a&gt;. While keeping a strong interest in computational neuroscience, my new endeavors will seek to adapt computationally efficient neural circuit mechanisms into AI architectures (such as deep neural networks) aiming for more flexible / powerful learning algorithms.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I am currently part of the 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.levydecisionlab.com&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Decision Lab&lt;/a&gt;, led by Ifat Levy. As a Postdoctoral Research Scientist, I collaborated with Nancy Kopell 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.bu.edu&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;(Boston University)&lt;/a&gt;, Thilo Womelsdorf 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.vanderbilt.edu&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;(Vanderbilt University)&lt;/a&gt;, and Xiao-Jing Wang 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.nyu.edu&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;(New York University)&lt;/a&gt;. I earned my PhD in Computational Neuroscience at the 
&lt;a href=&#34;http://in.umh-csic.es&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Neuroscience Institute (UMH-CSIC)&lt;/a&gt;, under the supervision of Albert Compte 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.clinicbarcelona.org/en/idibaps&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;(IDIBAPS – Hospital Clinic)&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;news&#34;&gt;News&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Openings: Stay tuned for an upcoming announcement of openings at the interface of Computational Neuroscience and AI.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PI Group Leader: I will start my own Lab at the Universitat Politècnica de València (UPV) in July 2020.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Grant: Distinguished Researcher Support Programme – GenT Plan Award (2020-2024).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
